This paper discusses techniques for Web data extraction, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for finding similarities between different versions of a Web page, which is related to database (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE) topics. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of wrappers, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) for extracting information from text.
